name: BANCO DE SABADELL, S.A.
bossPosition: Secretaria General y Vicesecretaria del Consejo de Administración
goal: Banco Sabadell is Spain’s fourth largest private banking group, comprised of different banks, brands, subsidiaries and part-owned companies covering all areas of the financial business sector, under a common denominator: professional performance and quality.
interests: Banking and financial services, Business and Industry, Climate Action, Competition, Consumers, Digital economy and society, Economy, finance and the euro, Fraud prevention, Institutional affairs, Taxation
euInitiatives: All European initiatives related to banking activity and with possible impacts on banks.
